    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:1.1",
          "pli": "… “Evameva kho, bhikkhave, appakā te sattā ye chedanavadhabandhanaviparāmosaālopasahasākārā paṭiviratā; atha kho eteva bahutarā sattā ye chedanavadhabandhanaviparāmosaālopasahasākārā appaṭiviratā. ",
          "en": "“… the sentient beings who refrain from mutilation, murder, abduction, banditry, plunder, and violence are few, while those who don’t refrain are many. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:1.2",
          "pli": "Taṃ kissa hetu? ",
          "en": "Why is that? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:1.3",
          "pli": "Adiṭṭhattā bhikkhave, catunnaṃ ariyasaccānaṃ. ",
          "en": "It’s because they haven’t seen the four noble truths. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:1.4",
          "pli": "Katamesaṃ catunnaṃ? ",
          "en": "What four? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:1.5",
          "pli": "Dukkhassa ariyasaccassa … pe … dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya ariyasaccassa. ",
          "en": "The noble truths of suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:2.1",
          "pli": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, ‘idaṃ dukkhan’ti yogo karaṇīyo … pe … ‘ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ti yogo karaṇīyo”ti. ",
          "en": "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:2.2",
          "pli": "Ekādasamaṃ. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:2.3",
          "pli": "Catutthaāmakadhaññapeyyālavaggo dasamo. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:3.1",
          "pli": "Khettaṃ kāyaṃ dūteyyañca, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:3.2",
          "pli": "tulākūṭaṃ ukkoṭanaṃ; ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:3.3",
          "pli": "Chedanaṃ vadhabandhanaṃ, ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn56.96-101:3.4",
          "pli": "viparālopaṃ sāhasanti. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
